{"tid":850534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵爆港　中國客：香港是後花園　以後不計劃了　隨時來　隨便來","createTime":"2018-10-06T14:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T17:27:17.000Z","uid":47714,"like":20,"dislike":399,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5fb6eac031897df2b06a5451c242bb63ed5500","tid":850534,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b8f8f8fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&h=85f4fa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20181004/480pix/1538660222_61d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20181004%2F480pix%2F1538660222_61d5.jpg&h=4e9b412e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VG1rh72aJJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVG1rh72aJJg&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d704a9df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VG1rh72aJJg</a><br />\n<br />\n李先生表示，高鐵開通增加其來港意慾：「因為它就像我們的後花園一樣，在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。以後想來就來，因為隨著這麼方便的高鐵開通以後，我們曾經要做的訪港計劃是不需要了，因為隨時可以買到票就可以走，不像以前我們還要計劃『十一』、『五一』這樣。」內地遊客郭先生亦表示高鐵很方便，但因為大部分時間也在穿過山洞，看不到風景，感覺比較像乘地鐵。"},{"pid":"9e18454fe9d46a9a02224a0858d86f4b1d9e349e","tid":850534,"uid":183758,"like":383,"dislike":5,"score":378,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"祝你哋全家生癌死"},{"pid":"6441d06c0fb28f110e401934cb3847f0fe505ca8","tid":850534,"uid":47714,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-phot