50534,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b8f8f8fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&h=85f4fa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20181004/480pix/1538660222_61d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20181004%2F480pix%2F1538660222_61d5.jpg&h=4e9b412e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VG1rh72aJJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVG1rh72aJJg&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d704a9df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VG1rh72aJJg</a><br />\n<br />\n李先生表示，高鐵開通增加其來港意慾：「因為它就像我們的後花園一樣，在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。以後想來就來，因為隨著這麼方便的高鐵開通以後，我們曾經要做的訪港計劃是不需要了，因為隨時可以買到票就可以走，不像以前我們還要計劃『十一』、『五一』這樣。」內地遊客郭先生亦表示高鐵很方便，但因為大部分時間也在穿過山洞，看不到風景，感覺比較像乘地鐵。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"受訪呢班真係斯斯文文, 唔係平時係上水見到果一種山番大陸人. <br />\n壹仔係咪揀過D受訪者? 曲線維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc3526cc3f1f4420739c802d6728f315777b4b3","tid":850534,"uid":107639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9d431715c628e503b71d3595ec0b1b7f2f3d229","tid":850534,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":100,"score":-94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。</span><br />\n<br />\n依一句  兒登仔 應該最啱聽架喎   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n威啦  疊水啦腥港  , 點解無正評既 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1